  "title": "Subway F&B Executive",
  "description": "<p><br>\n- To run and manage restaurant's daily operations</p>\n<p>- To ensure food safety- To ensure sales targets are achieved at all times</p>\n<p>- To optimize cost of goods</p>\n<p>- To perform stock take, ordering, and plan weekly roster</p>\n<p>- To ensure restaurant in compliance &amp; good maintenance</p>\n<p>- To ensure consistently high quality of customer service in all areas</p>\n<p>- To respond to complaints, taking appropriate actions to turn dissatisfied guests into return guests</p>\n<p>- To investigate and resolve complaints concerning food quality and service- To ensure effective and friendly communications with all supervisors and staffs and develop a happy and cheerful working relationship with all staffs</p>\n<p>- To maintain cohesiveness of the team to maximise positive teamwork efforts</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>The ability to inspire, motivate and lead a team<br>\nExcellent communication and people skills<br>\nA strong commitment to customer service<br>\nSelf-motivated and able to work in a fast paced environment<br>\nThe ability to work under pressure and handle challenging situations<br>\nConfidence, driven and passionate about F&amp;B<br>\nThe ability to understand and analyze sales figure and its cost implications<br>\nPlanning and organizational skills<br>\nKnowledge of IT preferred.<br>\nWilling to travel to different locations in Singapore<br>\nGood stamina with long standing hours<br>\nFlexible working hours<br>\nResponsible and independent<br>\n</p>",
